First prototype of a scrolling shooter.

Move with arrows
F key for fullscreen
P key for pause
M key for mute

plug in gamepads for up to 4 players

Windows users can download data and game.exe at :

https://91.121.141.56/owncloud/public.php?service=files&t=3feddd8c098bb12f54899651417bc6bb


Dependencies:
    python 2.7, pygame, numpy

    and to pack for windows :
        pyinstaller, pywin32

    MacOS:
        libvorbis
